{
  "title": "OneTrust System Reference Guide",
  "summary": "This article provides a comprehensive technical and operational overview of the OneTrust system within the context of the 3pi-v2 project. It details the system's role in managing Third-Party Interest (TPI) compliance, its integration with Aravo and Salesforce, and the critical data synchronization workflows required for automated risk management. The document serves as the authoritative source for understanding the system's architecture, historical evolution, and current operational status.",
  "infobox": {
    "type": "System",
